1. "*Ustaj* da bih ti pokazao kako se to radi!" (Get up so I can show you how to do it!)
2. "Nije vreme da *ustajemo*." (It's not time to get up.)
3. "Ovi ljudi se nikada neće *ustati* i promeniti stvari." (These people will never stand up and change things.)
4. "Ne možeš da *ustaneš* i odeš ako ne dobiješ dozvolu." (You can't stand up and leave if you don't get permission.)
5. "Oni su se *ustali* i otišli." (They stood up and left.)